reviewText: I warn you to stay away from this video. I is really bad!  For true Leo fans this is not something you should buy or rent but if you received it as gift- SELL SELL SELL! ok, well all this video contains is interviews with  random people talking about Leo. There is no real footage of Leo which is  probably why you wanted to see this. There is no point to this film except  to bore you with other people's opinions.
